  SUBROUTINE READ_FILE_NML (NDSI, NML_FILE, IERR)
!/
!/                  +-----------------------------------+
!/                  | WAVEWATCH III           NOAA/NCEP |
!/                  |           M. Accensi              |
!/                  |                                   |
!/                  |                        FORTRAN 90 |
!/                  | Last update :         15-May-2018 |
!/                  +-----------------------------------+
!/
!  1. Purpose :
